6. Please list three names of PhaseⅠ enzymes and three names of PhaseⅡ

   enzymes.


7. In the Rate Theory, what are the factors which contribute to peak

   broadening? Please illustrate your answers.


8. There are four steps involved to make a mass spectrometer produce mass

   spectra? Please briefly discuss your answers.




